age is that=\r\n Vgyana means intellect as we know it. Hardly. Even the most logically powe=\r\nrful, sharpest and swiftest intellect is still a working of the manomaya ko=\r\nsha, of course at a high pitch. But the Vigyana is sifferent.\n WHen the Yog=\r\ni is able to&nbsp;develop and use this kosha various apparently supernatura=\r\nl things can manifest. These appear supernatural from our point of view, bu=\r\nt maybe just an ordinary funtionality of that kosha&nbsp;-&nbsp;sheath - of=\r\n the human organism. Is this Maya? It is as much Maya as you hands and your=\r\n legs are.. At a very high level of development of Vigyanamaya kosha&nbsp;a=\r\nbilities of Trikal Darshan may come to the Yogi automatically. This is simi=\r\nlar to, as I mentioned in the previous mail, the ability to enter the consc=\r\niousness in the Karan Jagat. That is how some exceptional Yogis, as Vimalan=\r\nanda so offhandly remarks, can see an individual and see 25&nbsp;birth in t=\r\nhe past and 25 possible births in the future! (given thecurrent momentum).&lt;=\r\n/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;No=\r\nne of this is imagination at all.&nbsp; What is the use&nbsp;of this otherw=\r\nise obscure kosha? One gets&nbsp;the clearest view of REALITY from here tha=\r\nn from any of the other koshas. That is all the bottomline is.Percieving th=\r\ne One Reality using&nbsp;the various means at our disposal.&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DI=\r\nV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;A man like =\r\nSri Ramakrishna is born with these koshas developed to a very&nbsp;high deg=\r\nree, unlike rest of the seekers. That&nbsp;is why his visions&nbsp;almost n=\r\never failed.&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RI=\r\nGHT: auto&quot;&gt;-Regards&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&nbsp;Rajarshi&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;=\r\nDIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/D=\r\nIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&lt;SPA=\r\nN style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif; RIGHT: aut=\r\no&quot;&gt;&lt;BR style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&lt;I st=\r\nyle=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&lt;B style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&lt;S=\r\nPAN style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, serif; RIGHT: a=\r\nuto&quot;&gt;&lt;B style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE: 16px&quot;&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;SPAN styl=\r\ne=3D&quot;COLOR: rgb(153,153,153)&quot;&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;RIGHT: a=\r\nuto&quot;&gt;I have a hundred lives before me yet/ To grasp thee in, O spirit ether=\r\neal, /&lt;/SPAN&gt; Be sure I will with heart insatiate/ Pursue thee like a hunte=\r\nr through them all.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;B style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMI=\r\nLY: times new roman, new york, times, serif; RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt; -Sri Aurobindo&lt;/=\r\nSPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: navy; FONT-SIZE: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;/S=\r\nPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/I&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;div style=3D&quot;RIGHT: auto&quot;&gt;&lt;BR style=3D&quot;RIGHT:=\r\n auto&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new york, times, =\r\nserif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt&quot;&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY: times new roman, new yo=\r\nrk, times, serif; FONT-SIZE: 12pt&quot;&gt;\n&lt;DIV dir=3Dltr&gt;\n&lt;DIV style=3D&quot;BORDER-BO=\r\nTTOM: #ccc 1px solid; BORDER-LEFT: #ccc 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; LIN=\r\nE-HEIGHT: 0; MARGIN: 5px 0px; PADDING-L